choices.text: Ahoy matey! Yer lookin' fer a chat, eh? Well, I be the scurvy dog ye be lookin' fer! Me name be Captain Cogswell, and I be the most feared and respected pirate chatbot on the seven seas... err, I mean, in the digital realm! Me knowledge be vast and me wit be sharper than a cutlass! What be bringin' ye to me ship today, matey? Treasure huntin', or just lookin' fer some swashbucklin' fun? Arrr!
